Building Wesnoth dependencies
There are a number of dependency libraries required. 
- SDL 1.2 - https://github.com/blackberry/SDL
- SDL_image - Follow the instructions in the SDL_image subdirectory.
- SDL_mixer - Follow the instructions in the SDL_mixer subdirectory.
- SDL_net - Follow the instructions in the SDL_net subdirectory.
- SDL_ttf - Follow the instructions in the SDL_ttf subdirectory.
- TouchControlOverlay - https://github.com/blackberry/TouchControlOverlay
- glib - Follow the instructions in the glib subdirectory.
- pango - Follow the instructions in the pango subdirectory.
- pixman - Follow the instructions in the pixman subdirectory.
- cairo - Follow the instructions in the cairo subdirectory.

